T*
(ABSTRACT) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This note reformulates the post-purchase advertising problem as a contextual-bandit) Tj
T*
(ad filtering problem for an in-house demand-side platform \(DSP\). The objective is not) Tj
T*
(yet to solve real-time bidding end-to-end, but to construct a principled first layer) Tj
T*
(that selects a small set of promising ads from a large candidate pool under exploration,) Tj
T*
(cold-start, delayed feedback, and auction-induced selection bias. We define the decision) Tj
T*
(process, reward, logging requirements, offline evaluation protocol, and compare multiple) Tj
T*
(contextual-bandit algorithms: Disjoint LinUCB, Hybrid LinUCB, Linear Thompson Sampling,) Tj
T*
(Logistic/GLM Bandits, and Neural Bandits. The recommended first implementation is a) Tj
T*
(feature-based LinUCB/LinTS baseline with inverse-propensity-aware logging and a clear path) Tj
T*
(to hybrid and generalized-linear extensions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Scope) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The product surface is a post-purchase page in a car-rental booking service. A user has) Tj
T*
(just completed a reservation, so the system observes contextual variables such as car type,) Tj
T*
(area, rental duration, price, device, and possibly session history. The DSP owns a set of) Tj
T*
(ads, each with metadata such as category, target area, target car type, advertiser, budget,) Tj
T*
(and cold-start status. The filtering layer chooses a small set of ads to pass to the) Tj
T*
(bidding layer. The bidding layer then decides bid prices using value prediction, pacing,) Tj
T*
(and auction logic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document focuses on the filtering layer. It deliberately separates filtering from) Tj
T*
(bidding because RTB contains censored feedback, budget constraints, pacing, and strategic) Tj
T*
(auction effects that are not fully captured by a standard contextual bandit.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Decision Problem) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
