(Feature Design) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(A linear first model requires interactions to be explicit. A minimal feature map is:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(x_t\(a\)=.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The feature map should be versioned. Every logged decision must store the feature version,) Tj
T*
(eligible ad set, chosen set, ranking scores, and action probabilities or propensities.) Tj
T*
