T*
(Method | Strengths | Weaknesses | Recommended role) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Disjoint LinUCB | Simple, interpretable, per-ad parameters | Poor cold start; many ads imply) Tj
T*
(many matrices | Educational baseline only) Tj
T*
(Shared LinUCB | Simple; fast; transfers across ads; easy cold start | Linear assumption;) Tj
T*
(feature engineering required | First implementation) Tj
T*
(Hybrid LinUCB | Balances global transfer and arm-specific effects | More bookkeeping; more) Tj
T*
(parameters | Second-stage extension) Tj
T*
(Linear Thompson Sampling | Smooth exploration; shares LinUCB state | Requires sampling and) Tj
T*
(variance calibration | Main A/B comparison with LinUCB) Tj
T*
(Logistic/GLM Bandit | Better for binary rewards and calibration | More complex online) Tj
T*
(inference | Use after linear baseline diagnostics) Tj
T*
(Neural Bandit | Nonlinear representation power | Data hungry; uncertainty is hard | Later-) Tj
T*
(stage research track) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
