T*
() Tj
T*
(* Define production-grade schemas for contexts, ads, eligible sets, actions, propensities,) Tj
T*
(and outcomes.) Tj
T*
(* Implement a shared linear model abstraction with Sherman--Morrison updates for A^-1.) Tj
T*
(* Implement both LinUCB and Linear Thompson Sampling on the same feature store.) Tj
T*
(* Add semi-bandit top-K learning: update the model for each displayed ad with observed) Tj
T*
(reward.) Tj
T*
(* Add randomized logging traffic and propensity recording before claiming offline gains.) Tj
T*
(* Evaluate with reward@K, CTR@K, cumulative regret in simulation, IPS/SNIPS on logs, and) Tj
T*
(calibration plots.) Tj
T*
(* Introduce Hybrid LinUCB only after the shared model has stable logs and enough per-ad) Tj
T*
(observations.) Tj
T*
(* Keep the bidding layer separate: expected value from the filtering layer should become one) Tj
T*
(input to bid price,) Tj
T*
(together with pacing, budget, and bid shading.) Tj
